  <entry>
    <title>Hexo + NexT 搭建个人博客</title>
    <url>/2025/04/17/Hexo-NexT-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">创建页面</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page page_title</span><br><span class="line">创建文档</span><br><span class="line">hexo new text_title</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="分仓部署"><a href="#分仓部署" class="headerlink" title="分仓部署"></a>分仓部署</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new post &quot;XXX&quot;</span><br><span class="line"># 编辑 markdown 文件</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d     # 部署更新到 GitHub Pages</span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;更新笔记：XXX&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git push                           # 推送源码到源码仓库</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="Linux脚本"><a href="#Linux脚本" class="headerlink" title="Linux脚本"></a>Linux脚本</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;更新博客：$(date &#x27;+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S&#x27;)&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git push</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>运行</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bash blog-update.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="Windows脚本"><a href="#Windows脚本" class="headerlink" title="Windows脚本"></a>Windows脚本</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line">setlocal enabledelayedexpansion</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">:: 设置时间戳作为提交信息</span><br><span class="line">for /f %%i in (&#x27;powershell -Command &quot;Get-Date -Format \&quot;yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\&quot; &quot;&#x27;) do set commit_msg=更新博客：%%i</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">echo.</span><br><span class="line">echo ========= 1. 清理 Hexo 缓存 =========</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean || goto error</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">echo.</span><br><span class="line">echo ========= 2. 生成静态文件 =========</span><br><span class="line">hexo g || goto error</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">echo.</span><br><span class="line">echo ========= 3. 部署到 GitHub Pages =========</span><br><span class="line">hexo d || goto error</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">echo.</span><br><span class="line">echo ========= 4. 推送源码到 GitHub =========</span><br><span class="line">git add . || goto error</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;!commit_msg!&quot; || goto error</span><br><span class="line">git push || goto error</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">echo.</span><br><span class="line">echo ✅ 博客部署完成！</span><br><span class="line">goto end</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">:error</span><br><span class="line">echo ❌ 出现错误，任务中断，请检查上面日志。</span><br><span class="line">pause</span><br><span class="line">exit /b</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">:end</span><br><span class="line">pause</span><br><span class="line">exit</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>将上面内容保存为 <code>blog-update.bat</code>，放在Hexo 博客根目录下（和 <code>_config.yml</code> 同级）</p>
<p>双击运行即可，也可以在命令行运行 <code>blog-update.bat</code></p>
<h2 id="图片问题"><a href="#图片问题" class="headerlink" title="图片问题"></a>图片问题</h2><p>这是 Hexo 社区最主流的方式：每篇文章一个文件夹，文章和图片归在一起 ✨</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="🚀-步骤如下："><a href="#🚀-步骤如下：" class="headerlink" title="🚀 步骤如下："></a>🚀 步骤如下：</h3><h3 id="①-开启-Asset-文件夹功能"><a href="#①-开启-Asset-文件夹功能" class="headerlink" title="① 开启 Asset 文件夹功能"></a>① 开启 Asset 文件夹功能</h3><p>在 <code>hexo/_config.yml</code> 中加入或确认：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yaml</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">复制编辑</span><br><span class="line">post_asset_folder: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后，写文章的时候用：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">复制编辑</span><br><span class="line">hexo new post &quot;My-Post&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>它会自动创建结构如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bash复制编辑source/_posts/</span><br><span class="line">├── My-Post.md</span><br><span class="line">└── My-Post/           ← 图片放这里</span><br><span class="line">    └── image.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="②-插入图片（Markdown）"><a href="#②-插入图片（Markdown）" class="headerlink" title="② 插入图片（Markdown）"></a>② 插入图片（Markdown）</h3><p>在 <code>My-Post.md</code> 中这样引用图片：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">markdown</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">复制编辑</span><br><span class="line">![描述](My-Post/image.png)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>或者用 Hexo 自带的 asset_img 标签（需要启用 <code>hexo-renderer</code> 插件）：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">markdown</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">复制编辑</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% asset_img image.png 这是图片描述 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="📦-发布时会自动复制图片"><a href="#📦-发布时会自动复制图片" class="headerlink" title="📦 发布时会自动复制图片"></a>📦 发布时会自动复制图片</h2><p>运行 <code>hexo g</code> 或 <code>hexo d</code> 时，Hexo 会自动把 <code>source/_posts/文章名/</code> 里的图片复制到生成目录。</p>
]]></content>
